 â€¢ Use Role and RoleBinding when scoping permissions to a single namespaceâ€”ideal for multi-tenant environments.
 â€¢ Use ClusterRole and ClusterRoleBinding for cluster-wide permissions or resources that aren't namespace-scoped.
 â€¢ Avoid broad or wildcard permissions unless absolutely necessary.

