 â€¢ Use kubectl auth can-i to test what a user or service account can do.
 â€¢ Regularly audit RoleBindings and ClusterRoleBindings to prevent permission creep.
 â€¢ Use service accounts with minimal permissions for CI/CD pipelines and automation tools.
 â€¢ Consider third-party tools like rakkess, kubeaudit, or OPA Gatekeeper for deeper RBAC insights and policies.

